song_name: Im In Love With A German Film Star

version_description: Changed chords slightly so it sounds a bit better than the others.
Sounds more accurate when played alone on acoustic guitar.
From Dave Grohl's acoustic solo performance: https://youtu.be/oojkmef3hKg use this for strumming pattern.

I always play this version and I think it sounds better and more original than the others.
